very nice , would buy again.
very cool glass . great colour and aroma and mouthfeel .

very good saison, the best .
complex aroma, close your eyes and you are walking through a spring field in the Belgian countryside . fresh , florally, can almost hear the birds chirping in this one ! beautiful sharp carbination, creating big white fluffy creamy head and such a lovely golden colour . tastes like you should buy one and find out for yourself ;)

you will really enjoy this if you like saison ale
am hoping to turn into a werewolf after drinking this beer . it is supposed to be brewed on the full moon , fingers crossed :)

wow, no really , Wow! what a sexy beer . fantastic label. great aroma, delicate hints of whiskey, raisins, Christmas cake, as dark as dark can get . lovely soft carbination with a small but fluffy caramel head and a such a smoothing gentle mouth feel again with whiskey like flavours , bit sour , sweet and pleasing . will miss this when its gone :(
beer_name: Flying Dog Wild Dog Barrel-Aged Gonzo
